      "text": "こんなに素晴らしい景色を見ることが出来て……\nアイドルを続けてきて良かった……諦めなくて良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.6999972026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.4680066744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ここがゴールじゃありません。この優勝で\n満足することなく、私達はさらに上を目指します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2150927225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
