      "text": "三人の努力を、私達はずっと近くで見てたから……\n誰よりも頑張ってきたトリエルが報われて嬉しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2000160217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.9089498993
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_11_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "きっとトリエルの優勝に勇気づけられた人は沢山いる\nトリエルはみんなの希望の翼になったんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.9000160217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
